post_text:
Middle School March Students of the Month: We are pleased to announce the Middle School Students of the Month for March. These students were nominated by their teachers and the finalists were selected by a school committee. Congratulations to these students and their families on this well-deserved recognition.

From left to right: Addison Liwacz, Elk Student of the Month;
Trinity Wescott, 8th Grade Student of the Month;
Yining Lin, 7th Grade Student of the Month.

